170
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:47,300
- Have a seat. - Yes, sir.

171
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,270
Was it enjoyable?

172
00:11:51,140 --> 00:11:52,870
- Sorry? - After letting WIND...

173
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:55,909
take a plunge like this,

174
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:58,110
