never recovered since COVID-19.

181
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:15,460
Not that again!

182
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:17,630
You...

183
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:19,599
- Remember what I said? - Sorry?

184
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,600
Seriously?

185
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:23,869
Get out there and see
the situation at Han River.

186
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,710
There are bicycles everywhere!

187
00:12:26,770 --> 00:12:27,780
Sir, please.

188
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,350
You're the CEO,

189
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:41,660
