199
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:47,120
Yes, I think he's at the head office.

200
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:48,759
To see the chairman?

201
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:49,920
Yes, it seems that way.

202
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:52,189
