213
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,960
CEO Oh, it's rough, isn't it?

214
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:38,670
- You're here. - Hello.

215
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,110
Would you like some coffee?

216
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:42,209
