222
00:15:06,730 --> 00:15:08,170
Wasn't it doing well?

223
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:11,069
After WIND was bought in 2015,

224
00:15:11,070 --> 00:15:13,539
it had its ups and downs.

225
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:15,379
But since 2021 up to last year,

226
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:18,080
it saw a 30-percent
increase in sales every year.

227
00:15:18,410 --> 00:15:19,450
Hold on.

228
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,319
Manufacturing bicycles
isn't like the IT business.

229
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,190
So a 30-percent increase every year?

230
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:27,319
A lot of my friends are
members of cycling clubs.

231
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,759
Exactly. It was the craze.

232
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:31,959
Now that you think about it,
COVID-19 gave it a huge boost.

233
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,759
At the time, there were
great expectations...

234
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,300
about the sports and leisure industry.

235
00:15:35,530 --> 00:15:36,960
It was my mistake.

236
00:15:38,730 --> 00:15:40,129
Cycling is a sport...

237
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:42,500
