while the market was still hot.

246
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:12,330
It seems a bit too late now.

247
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:14,240
Forget about Director Lee,

248
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:18,210
and tell me what you think.

249
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:20,310
I believe...

250
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:24,010
