no for you too. Am I right?

261
00:16:53,010 --> 00:16:54,040
Yes, sir.

262
00:17:05,620 --> 00:17:06,950
Is he faint-hearted?

263
00:17:07,320 --> 00:17:08,320
Pardon?

264
00:17:12,590 --> 00:17:13,989
Can't Director Ha just go to Samoel...

265
00:17:13,990 --> 00:17:15,530
